Name: degenerative myopia
Definition: A syndrome that is characterized by papulonodular skin lesions containing a proliferation of true macrophages associated with arthritis.

Name: obsolete nephrotic syndrome with lesion of membranoproliferative glomerulonephritis
Definition: A syndrome that is characterized by papulonodular skin lesions containing a proliferation of true macrophages associated with arthritis.
Synonym: Nephrotic syndrome with lesion of membranoproliferative glomerulonephritis
